snippet.title: WOW! Celebrity Family Feud Season 4 FAST MONEY MARATHON! | Celebrity Family Feud
snippet.description:
Here they are! We've got all the epic, edge of your seat moments... The crazy comebacks and the awesome wins and brutal losses during Fast Money on this season's Celebrity Family Feud with Steve Harvey. Check out Kanye West, Kim Kardashian-West, Shaq, Charles Barkley, Jeff Dunham and many more of your favorite celebrities as they play for $25,000 for their favorite charities!
